OL,5,C` survey
OL,7,FOne in five Britons have ended or
OL,8,Fwould consider ending a romantic or
OL,9,Fplatonic relationship because of
OL,10,Fsalary differences, according to a
OL,11,Fsurvey for Nationwide.
OL,13,FThe average wage gap between friends
OL,14,Fand partners has reached #32,000, the
OL,15,Fpoll suggests.
