OL,7,FMore than one in 10 (12%) say they
OL,8,Fworry conversations about money could
OL,9,Fresult in conflict.
OL,11,FIn order to cope with financial
OL,12,Ftensions and avoid conversations, 10%
OL,13,Fsay they have had to cancel plans or
OL,14,Fdelay major money decisions and 7% say
OL,15,Fthey have lied about their income.
