OL,4,Crelationship over difference in salary
OL,5,C` survey
OL,7,FSome 42% say they have faced negative
OL,8,Fconsequences after raising an issue
OL,9,Faround money, including stress and
OL,10,Fanxiety, feelings of resentment, or a
OL,11,Fchange in their relationship's power
OL,12,Fdynamic.
OL,14,FHowever, 33% said that openly
OL,15,Fdiscussing their finances had
OL,16,Fstrengthened their relationships.
