OL,3,COne in five Britons would end
OL,4,Crelationship over difference in salary
OL,5,C` survey
OL,7,FPsychotherapist Kamalyn Kaur said:
OL,8,F"Open financial conversations are not
OL,9,Fabout comparing salaries, they are
OL,10,Fabout aligning values, setting
OL,11,Frealistic expectations, respecting
OL,12,Fboundaries, and protecting emotional
OL,13,Fwellbeing on both sides.
